{
  "stem": "5275.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I took them to my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he still would work on the films.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But it became very dangerous, because people were coming to the apartment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the Gestapo was coming in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we had to disassemble the table, took out all the thing, and covered it with a plywood, and put things on it, so it wouldn't be seen that it was a table.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well one day, a number of Germans-- and I don't even think they were Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I think they were just Wehrmacht, the Army, maybe there was Gestapo, SS-- just came into the apartment and started rummaging around.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And after a while, they just left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then, after that, we found out there was a number of things missing, like crystal.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They came in with big coats, with big pockets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And apparently, whenever they saw a crystal vase or something, they just put it into their pocket.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So that was another of my early experiences with the Germans, at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The next memory was the-- well, the declaration that ghetto was being established, and all the Jews had to move to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My mother, who did not look Jewish, didn't want to go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But my father was much older.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He didn't want to hide.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He felt he could not do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he said, no, we have to go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And since I lived with my father, my mother was not able to support me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "My mother decided to move into the ghetto with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The day we went, my mother took a-- what do you call those?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like in Central Park, in New York, with the horse drawn carriage, you know, they have New York park?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, Warsaw was full of those.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
